comment_data.body:
@ruslo How can we remove BuildLibuv.cmake completely, when we have a Windows-specific patch for libuv?

https://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/418abfc9d06923e96f1317419fe83ed4e6d67c1d/third-party/cmake/BuildLibuv.cmake#L45-L48

We have similar patches for other dependencies and have specifically used the patching functionality instead of creating our own forks for each project.
